        "synopsis": {
            "value": "When Baek Ah-Jin (Kim You-Jung) was little, she endured domestic violence. To survive, she learned to hide her emotions and manipulate others by seeing into their hearts. She is normally generous and kind to people, but she reveals her devilish side if someone angers her or for her own purposes. With her beautiful appearance and her mastered talents, she is now a top actress. She has Yoon Jun-Seo (Kim Young-Dae), who has been by her side all of her life and he is willing to do anything for her. He is the only one who she can rely and feel comfortable with, but, for Baek Ah-Jin, he decides to bring about her downfall.\n\nMeanwhile, Kim Jae-Oh (Kim Do-Hoon) is also a man who has been by Baek Ah-Jin’s side his whole life. He suffered abuse from his father and felt a connection with Baek Ah-Jin. Through her, he found a reason to live. Le-Na (Lee Yul-Eum) is a top actress, who is a former idol. She has feelings for Yoon Jun-Seo.",
